Meta description: The sounds coming from machines often provide important clues that may be missed by relying on vibration data alone. The A647BT wireless Bluetooth headphones can be worn comfortably with a hardhat and the 23 db NRR will serve as hearing protection.

Meta description: With Emerson´s AMS EZ 1000 eddy current sensor and converter you always have the part you need when you need it. With one converter that is compatible with a range of sensors and cables, you’ll be able to mix-and-match your spares to your application while reducing your converter inventory. And with an easy-to-use procedure for field calibrations, you’ll be back to work sooner. The AMS EZ 1000 makes changing out sensors following a shutdown or replacing sensors during turnarounds/maintenance quick and painless.
Short Description: With Emerson´s AMS EZ 1000 eddy current sensor and converter you always have the part you need when you need it. With one converter that is compatible with a range of sensors and cables, you’ll be able to mix-and-match your spares to your application while reducing your converter inventory. And with an easy-to-use procedure for field calibrations, you’ll be back to work sooner. The AMS EZ 1000 makes changing out sensors following a shutdown or replacing sensors during turnarounds/maintenance quick and painless.
